#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid "Course:"
msgstr "Kurs:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid "A course is associated to one language and contains a list of units."
msgstr "Kurs je povezan s jednim jezikom i sadrži listu jedinica."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unit:"
msgstr "Jedinica:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A unit consists of phrases that are \"somehow\" homogeneous. E.g. those can "
"be phrases spoken in a restaurant or phrases spoken at a conversation at the "
"street by a tourist searching for the way."
msgstr ""
"Jedinica se sastoji od fraza  \"somehow\" homogeneous. E.g. to mogu biti "
"fraze koje se koriste u restoranu ili u razgovaoru na ulici sa turistima "
"koji pokušavaju pronaći put."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:303
#, no-c-format
msgid "Course Skeletons:"
msgstr "Skeletoni Kursa:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A course skeleton forms the prototype of a course. This is, skeletons help "
"to ease creation of courses in several languages as they state a set of "
"units and phrases (in English) that then can be used as a blueprint to "
"create a course in a new language. Updates of course skeletons can also be "
"imported into courses that are created from a skeleton."
msgstr ""
"Skeleton kursa formira prototip kursa. Ovo je, skeleton pomaže u kreacijama "
"kursa u više jezika koje sadrže više jedinica i fraza (na Engleskom) onda se "
"može koristiti kao blueprint da biste kreirali novi kurs na novom jeziku. "
"Update skeletona kursa može također biti uvezen u kurs koji je kreiran iz "
"skeletona."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid "Phrases:"
msgstr "Fraze:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:315
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Phrases are given by a text string and a recording by a native speaker. We "
"differ phrases by their lengths. The following phrase lengths exists"
msgstr ""
"Fraze su date kao tekst i snimljene u nativnom izgovoru. Dijelimo fraze "
"prema dužini trajanja. Slijedeće trajanje fraze postoji."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid "word: a single word, letter, or number"
msgstr "word:riječ, pismo, ili broj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:326
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"expression: an expression of several words that does not form a complete "
"sentence"
msgstr "izrazi:jedan izraz od više riječi koji ne popunjava kompletu rečenicu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid "sentence: a complete sentence"
msgstr "rečenica: kompletna rečenica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:338
#, no-c-format
msgid "paragraph: several sentences (usually 2-3)"
msgstr "paragraf: više rečenica (uobičajno 2-3)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:347
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A course is associated with a specific language, consists of different units "
"and each unit is given by a sequence of phrases in different lengths."
msgstr ""
"Kurs je povezan sa specifičnim jezikom, sadrži različite jedinice i svaka "
"jednica je data po sekvenci fraze različitog trajanja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set Storage Folder/Course Repository"
msgstr "Uspostavi Folder za Skladištenje/Kurs Spremišta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:354
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The editor operates within a separate folder (in the following called "
"<emphasis>repository</emphasis>, as it is recommended to be under some "
"version control system). In that folder, the editor searches for editable "
"courses and skeleton files and also stores new files."
msgstr ""
"Uređivač radi sa odvojenim direktorijima (u daljnjem naziv "
"<emphasis>skladište</emphasis>, kao što je preporučeno da bude pod nekim "
"sistemom kontrole).U tom folderur, uređivač traži kursove za uređivanje i "
"skeletonske fajlove i čuvanje fajlova."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The course repository can be set in the configuration dialog. It can be "
"found at <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure "
"&artikulate;</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and the course settings are at the "
"menu option <guilabel>Course Resources</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Predstavljanje kursa može biti postavljeno u konfiguracijskom dijalogu. Može "
"se pronaći u <menuchoice><guimenu>Postavke</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Konfiguracija  &artikulate;</guimenuitem></menuchoice>i "
"postavke kursa su u opcijama izbornika <guilabel>Izvori Kursa</guilabel>."

